<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>出版物 |皮尤研究中心</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/publications/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 12:33:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>谁认为自己的一方在政治上获胜或失败，党派分歧严重</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/24/stark-partisan-divide-in-who-thinks-their-side-is-winning-and-losing-in-politics/</link><description>在我们提出这个问题的十年里，美国人总体上更有可能说他们的球队正在输，而不是说他们赢了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 12:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/24/stark-partisan-divide-in-who-thinks-their-side-is-winning-and-losing-in-politics/</guid></item><item><title>青少年如何使用和看待人工智能</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/internet/2026/02/24/how-teens-use-and-view-ai/</link><description>超过一半的美国青少年表示他们曾使用聊天机器人来帮助完成学业，12% 的青少年表示他们从这些工具中获得了情感支持。青少年倾向于更积极地看待人工智能未来对他们生活的影响，而不是消极地看待。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 12:18:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/internet/2026/02/24/how-teens-use-and-view-ai/</guid></item><item><title>2026 年国情咨文：美国人在国家面临的关键问题上的立场</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/23/state-of-the-union-2026-where-americans-stand-on-key-issues-facing-the-nation/</link><description>在国情咨文发布之前，以下是根据皮尤研究中心最近的调查得出的美国公众对关键政策问题的看法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 12:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/23/state-of-the-union-2026-where-americans-stand-on-key-issues-facing-the-nation/</guid></item><item><title>电子邮件通讯作为新闻来源</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/journalism/2026/02/19/email-newsletters-as-a-source-of-news/</link><description>十分之三的美国成年人表示，他们至少有时会从时事通讯中获取新闻，但许多人并没有阅读他们收到的大部分时事通讯。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Feb 2026 12:28:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/journalism/2026/02/19/email-newsletters-as-a-source-of-news/</guid></item><item><title>美国哪些宗教团体受教育程度最高？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/19/which-us-religious-groups-are-most-highly-educated/</link><description>印度教徒和犹太人比其他宗教团体的美国人更有可能获得四年制大学学位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Feb 2026 12:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/19/which-us-religious-groups-are-most-highly-educated/</guid></item><item><title>是什么让人们为自己的国家感到自豪？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/02/17/what-makes-people-proud-of-their-country/</link><description>从印度尼西亚的多样性到法国的美食，25 个国家的人们用自己的语言分享了令他们感到自豪的事情。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Feb 2026 12:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/02/17/what-makes-people-proud-of-their-country/</guid></item><item><title>关于美国民族自豪感的 6 个事实</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/17/6-facts-about-national-pride-in-the-us/</link><description>共和党人和民主党人倾向于强调不同的自豪感来源——这种党派分歧在大多数其他国家并不那么明显。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Feb 2026 12:21:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/17/6-facts-about-national-pride-in-the-us/</guid></item><item><title>哪些国家的公共假期最多和最少？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/12/which-countries-have-the-most-and-fewest-public-holidays/</link><description>在我们分析的 190 个联合国成员国中，典型国家将在 2026 年庆祝 13 个公共假期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Feb 2026 01:44:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/12/which-countries-have-the-most-and-fewest-public-holidays/</guid></item><item><title>美国人如何看待特朗普政府的主要成员</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/12/how-americans-view-key-members-of-the-trump-administration/</link><description>58% 的大多数人表示他们对唐纳德·特朗普总统持负面看法，40% 的人持正面看法。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Feb 2026 01:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/02/12/how-americans-view-key-members-of-the-trump-administration/</guid></item><item><title>世界各地的宗教多样性</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/02/12/religious-diversity-around-the-world/</link><description>截至 2020 年，新加坡是宗教多元化程度最高的国家，也门则是宗教多元化程度最低的国家。美国在人口众多的国家中排名第一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Feb 2026 01:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/02/12/religious-diversity-around-the-world/</guid></item></channel></rss>